        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="step-box">
          <i class="bi bi-collection"></i>
          <h5>2. Explore</h5>
          <p>Browse through verified and detailed listings across multiple categories.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="step-box">
          <i class="bi bi-chat-dots"></i>
          <h5>3. Connect</h5>
